'''MPEG LA'''是一家位於[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[丹佛市|丹佛市]]，從事[[專利|專利]]授權的[[有限公司|有限公司]]，主要從事標準[[專利池|專利池]]的授權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mpegla.com/main/Pages/About.aspx|title=Revolutionizing Intellectual Property Rights Management|accessdate=2010-04-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/671UAj2U4?url=http://www.mpegla.com/main/Pages/About.aspx|archive-date=2012-04-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{citation |url=http://www.osnews.com/story/23236/Why_Our_Civilization_s_Video_Art_and_Culture_is_Threatened_by_the_MPEG-LA |title=Why Our Civilization's Video Art and Culture is Threatened by the MPEG-LA |first=Eugenia |last=Loli-Queru |date=2010-05-01 |publisher=OSNews |accessdate=2014-09-07 |archive-date=2018-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181126015745/http://www.osnews.com/story/23236/Why_Our_Civilization_s_Video_Art_and_Culture_is_Threatened_by_the_MPEG-LA |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

其擁有了不少重要的[[多媒體|多媒體]]標準專利，包含了如[[MPEG-2|MPEG-2]]<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.eetimes.com/showArticle.jhtml;jsessionid=WHQGCDCQAPPDCQSNDLOSKH0CJUNN2JVN?articleID=197801387 |date=2007-03-12 |first=Mike |last=Clendenin |title=Chinese set-top box makers, MPEG LA face off over patent fees |publisher=EE Times |accessdate=2014-09-07 |archive-date=2012-09-12 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120912162333/http://www.eetimes.com/showArticle.jhtml;jsessionid=WHQGCDCQAPPDCQSNDLOSKH0CJUNN2JVN?articleID=197801387 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[MPEG-4|MPEG-4]] Visual （Part 2）、[[IEEE_1394|IEEE 1394]]、[[VC-1|VC-1]]、[[ATSC|ATSC]]、{{link-en|多視圖編碼|Multiview Video Coding|MVC}}、[[MPEG2-TS|MPEG2-TS]]、[[H.264/MPEG-4_AVC|AVC/H.264]]以及[[HEVC|HEVC]]等等。MPEG LA也提供了[[無線網狀網路|無線網狀網路]]技術的專利授權。

MPEG LA與[[MPEG|MPEG]]組織（Moving Picture Experts Group）並無直接的關聯。

==歷史==
MPEG LA是在收到[[美國司法部|美國司法部]]企業審查信函（Business Review Letter）後，與1997年7月開始營運<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.justice.gov/atr/public/busreview/215742.htm|title=MPEG LA Business Review Letter|accessdate=2013-05-13|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109070322/http://www.justice.gov/atr/public/busreview/215742.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[MPEG-2|MPEG-2]]標準制定的期間，一群參與制定的公司了解到MPEG-2標準要被採用的最大困難，來自於基礎專利是被許多專利擁有者所持有。最終八個MPEG-2專利的擁有者 -- [[富士通|富士通]]、[[松下電器|松下電器]]、[[索尼|索尼]]、[[三菱集團|三菱集團]]、{{link-en|Scientific Atlanta|Scientific Atlanta}}、[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]、[[飛利浦|飛利浦]]以及[[通用儀器|通用儀器]] -- 再加上{{link-en|CableLabs|CableLabs}}和一些個體戶，一同成立了MPEG LA並接著創立了第一個現行的專利池解決方案。

在2012年6月，MPEG LA發表了[[High_Efficiency_Video_Coding|High Efficiency Video Coding（HEVC）]]標準的基礎專利需求<ref>{{Cite press release |url=http://www.mpegla.com/Lists/MPEG%20LA%20News%20List/Attachments/82/n-12-06-26.pdf |title=MPEG LA Announces Call for Patents Essential to High Efficiency Video Coding (HEVC) |publisher=MPEG LA |location=Denver, CO |format=PDF |date=2012-06-26 |accessdate=2013-05-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514055624/http://www.mpegla.com/Lists/MPEG%20LA%20News%20List/Attachments/82/n-12-06-26.pdf |archivedate=2013-05-14 }}</ref>。

